    <string name="des0">Welcome to My Accounts! Your personalized tool to manage and improve your personal finances. Start your journey today towards a healthy and secure financial life.</string>
    <string name="des1">Create your profile to access the app and ensure the confidentiality of your records, which are securely stored on your mobile device. Create your profile now for a personalized and protected experience!</string>
    <string name="des2">Add accounts during the profile setup process or at any time afterward. You can choose any currency in the world and change it whenever you wish. When changing currencies, you can choose to update all your transactions to the new format or just the currency format.</string>
    <string name="des3">To manage your finances effectively, record your income and expenses daily for each account. You can also transfer funds between your accounts using the transactions option.</string>
    <string name="des4">Check your financial progress through detailed charts. Bar graphs show your monthly income, expenses, and balance, while pie charts give you a clear view of how your expenses are distributed across categories over a set period.</string>
    <string name="des5">Easily check transactions by searching by name, date range, or amount, so you can keep a detailed track of all your transactions.</string>
    <string name="des6">Monitor both your total spending and spending by category over a specific period. Enable notifications to receive alerts when you reach your spending limits and keep your finances under control.</string>

